    {
      "type": "warmup",
      "content": "<h2>Warm-up (2-3 min)</h2>\n<p>Yesterday&#39;s vocabulary:</p>\n<pre><code>motive → ?     result → ?\ncause → ?      reason → ?\n</code></pre>\n<p>(Answers: <code>mukti</code>, <code>jalge</code>, <code>rinka</code>, <code>krinu</code>)</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "material",
      "content": "<h2>New Material (5-7 min)</h2>\n<h3>New Vocabulary</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Lojban</th>\n<th>Place Structure</th>\n<th>English</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>gasnu</code></td>\n<td>x1 (agent) causes/brings about x2</td>\n<td>make happen</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>zukte</code></td>\n<td>x1 does/acts to bring about x2</td>\n<td>do/act</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>troci</code></td>\n<td>x1 tries to do x2</td>\n<td>try</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>snada</code></td>\n<td>x1 succeeds in doing x2</td>\n<td>succeed</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Doing and Acting</h3>\n<pre><code>mi zukte ti\n</code></pre>\n<p>I do this.</p>\n<pre><code>do zukte ma\n</code></pre>\n<p>What do you do? (What action do you take?)</p>\n<h3>Causing as Agent</h3>\n<pre><code>mi gasnu lo nu ti slabu\n</code></pre>\n<p>I bring about this being old. (I make this old.)</p>\n<p>Note: <code>gasnu</code> = agent causes, <code>rinka</code> = event causes.</p>\n<h3>Trying and Succeeding</h3>\n<pre><code>mi troci lo nu klama\n</code></pre>\n<p>I try to go.</p>\n<pre><code>mi snada lo nu gunka\n</code></pre>\n<p>I succeed in working.</p>\n<h3>Key Point</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>zukte</code> = do/act, <code>gasnu</code> = make happen, <code>troci</code> = try, <code>snada</code> = succeed.</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
      "title": "New Material (5-7 min)"
    },
    {
      "type": "practice",
      "content": "<h2>Practice (4-5 min)</h2>\n<h3>Exercise 1: Doing</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I do this.</li>\n<li>What do you do?</li>\n<li>Bob does that.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>mi zukte ti</code></li>\n<li><code>do zukte ma</code></li>\n<li><code>la .bob. cu zukte ta</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 2: Trying</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I try to go.</li>\n<li>She tries to work.</li>\n<li>We try to understand.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>mi troci lo nu klama</code></li>\n<li><code>ri troci lo nu gunka</code></li>\n<li><code>mi&#39;o troci lo nu jimpe</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Exercise 3: Succeeding</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I succeed.</li>\n<li>Bob succeeds in learning.</li>\n<li>Do you succeed?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>mi snada</code></li>\n<li><code>la .bob. cu snada lo nu cilre</code></li>\n<li><code>xu do snada</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>",
